d I am thankful for the opportunity to do so today. Question put and agreed to. Resolved, That this House has considered the future of the European Medicines Agency.     Share           3.50 pm          Sitting suspended.                    ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
